					<p class="lede text">Love Me Beauty approached me with a business concept. Through listening and asking the right questions, we drew up a collaborative scope for everything we'd need to launch.</p>
					 <p class="text">Every project has to begin at the end: with your users. In LMB's case, I used existing analytics and some custom extras (like the fantastic <a href="http://www.gosquared.com" target="_blank">GoSquared</a>) to get a really great idea of who the users were, why they visited, and what they wanted. From this, I could construct thoughtful and detailed User Personas – representative of key demographics who were currently using the site.</p>
